OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry night
OL,6,Fto come with clear spells. Breezy in
OL,7,Fthe southwest, but light winds
OL,8,Felsewhere. Mist and fog likely across
OL,9,Fcentral and eastern areas, which can
OL,10,Fbecome extensive by the morning.
OL,11,FFeeling chilly with a rural frost in
OL,12,Fplaces.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FAny mist, fog and low cloud in
OL,15,Fthe east will clear quickly after the
OL,16,Fsunrise. Another bright and sunny day
OL,17,Fexpected with temperatures slightly
OL,18,Fhigher than Thursday. Generally less
OL,19,Fwindy.
